data.description: This charming 4-bedroom, 2 bathroom house is your gateway to the Florida dream lifestyle. Located in a revitalized Riviera Beach neighborhood, enojy the  perfect blend of peaceful living and exciting potential. Outside, your own private oasis awaits. Unwind on the expansive fenced-in backyard, perfect for barbecues, yard games, or simply soaking up the sunshine. The best part...You're just a 10-minute drive from the beach! This home has HURRICANE WINDOWS throughout and a NEW ROOF will be finished prior to closing. Call and schedule your private showing today! First-Time Homebuyer Grant-Please speak with our preferred lender for more information: Beatriz Arteaga / Vice City Lending NMLS #2021088
